text: @FedEx @FedExHelp A package addressed to former resident was delivered over two weeks ago. I have called four times for pickup. Each time I'm told it will be picked up tomorrow. Then no one picks it up.  Help me get this package off my porch and to the intended recipient.
@crbickhaus Hi Chris, this is Julie. I am so sorry to hear this. I will be happy to assist you today. Please DM the tracking number, your address and contact phone number. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r
